<p>Are you tired of sending <strong>200+ applications</strong> and getting <strong>zero interviews</strong>?</p>

<p><strong>RequireHire.com</strong> is changing how people find jobs — especially in India right now.</p>

<p>It's an <strong>interview-first</strong> platform:</p>

<ul class="check-list">
  <li>Companies see your real interview performance first</li>
  <li>Skip endless forms and keyword filters</li>
  <li>Most features are completely free for candidates</li>
  <li>Verified profiles build more recruiter trust</li>
</ul>

<div class="note">
  <strong>2026 reality check:</strong> Your voice, confidence, and answers matter far more than resume formatting. RequireHire puts your actual skills in the spotlight.
</div>

<h2>How Easy It Is to Use (Step-by-Step – 2026)</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Visit <a href="https://www.requirehire.com/" target="_blank">requirehire.com</a></li>
  <li>Click “on login/ sign in as employee / employer on top right corner ” (Google / email / phone / resume as well  – under 45 seconds)</li>
  <li>Add basic info  (optional – AI extracts most details)</li>
  <li>Complete 1–2 short AI mock interviews (voice + camera, very realistic)</li>
  <li>Get your Skill Score & Profile Badge</li>
  <li>Recruiters discover you → real interview invites arrive</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Total time to become visible to recruiters:</strong> usually <strong>10–15 minutes</strong>.</p>

